This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

This fixed-blade survival knife is designed to withstand being used as both a weapon and a tool, such as for setting traps, hunting animals or cutting foliage. The handle is wrapped in a length of multi-purpose paracord. It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.\n\nA little color never hurt anyone
